{"tid":1038804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】佛州搗國際賣淫集團封「骨場」 拘捕8名中國女子","createTime":"2019-02-27T03:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T00:44:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":88,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa1044eb0572db1f9feb750f3ce4a9a51049763","tid":1038804,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:12:20.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達州警方掃黃，搗破涉及中國人的國際賣淫集團，拘捕8名中國女子。<br />\n8人年齡介乎27至58歲，被控敲詐勒索、依靠賣淫收入維生、賣淫等罪。<br />\n警方經過8個月的「放蛇」行動，拘捕逾200人，查封至少12間以按摩院為幌子的淫窟。美式足球超級碗應屆冠軍新英倫愛國者（New England Patriots）77歲老闆克拉夫特（Robert Kraft），早前被警方在一間按摩院內安裝的攝錄機拍到兩度與女子性交易，被控教唆賣淫。<br />\n有佛州人表示，丘辟特（Jupiter）有不少掛羊頭賣狗肉的「按摩院」，不諳英語，只操普通話或廣東話的中國女子在工作。警方視她們為販運人口受害者，指她們由中國抵美後，終日被困在按摩院，被迫賣淫。<br />\n警方懷疑該人口販運集團在紐約以至中國有同黨，涉及2,000萬美元（1.56億港元）。當局着手充公當中200至300萬美元（1,560至2,340萬港元）財產。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190227/large/1551206887_490b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190227%2Flarge%2F1551206887_490b.jpg&h=a0d9cb26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190227/59307599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190227%2F59307599&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6WWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=bcc3dfe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190227%2F59307599&h=84ba060d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190227/59307599</a>"},{"pid":"7fd503be98b6ef8aec5ddc9cdcb09bb1e2370c18","tid":1038804,"uid":136186,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"咁嘅樣都有得賣淫 有冇咁飢渴啊"},{"pid":"9579db04d0855ff39adfa7583e7eaf32329a8346","tid":1038804,"uid":77277,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"7fd503be98b6ef8aec5ddc9cdcb09bb1e2370c18","tid":1038804,"uid":1361